description:
User is logged in their account and is able to transfer some amount
    to another account.

elements.name: User is able to pay bill.

steps.name: The user lands at the webpage.
The user is logged in successfully.
The user navigates to bill pay tab.
Enters "<Payee Name>", "<Address>", "<City>", "<State>", "<Zip Code>", "<Phone Number>", "<Account Number>", "<Verify Account>", "<Amount>"
Selects account number, pressing the send payment.

name: User is able to transfer funds to an account.
